{"tid":2250951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明報 - 工程師否認城巴插33刀謀殺女友 控方：「控制狂」被告分手後性愛片段威脅事主","createTime":"2020-10-20T12:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T01:16:51.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"59f88c6025e039daec346b1ff396c3bf3baaf38d","tid":2250951,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:42:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201020/s00001/1603191596513/%e5%b7%a5%e7%a8%8b%e5%b8%ab%e5%90%a6%e8%aa%8d%e5%9f%8e%e5%b7%b4%e6%8f%9233%e5%88%80%e8%ac%80%e6%ae%ba%e5%a5%b3%e5%8f%8b-%e6%8e%a7%e6%96%b9-%e3%80%8c%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6%e7%8b%82%e3%80%8d%e8%a2%ab%e5%91%8a%e5%88%86%e6%89%8b%e5%be%8c%e6%80%a7%e6%84%9b%e7%89%87%e6%ae%b5%e5%a8%81%e8%84%85%e4%ba%8b%e4%b8%bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00001%2F1603191596513%2F%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%25a8%258b%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e5%2590%25a6%25e8%25aa%258d%25e5%259f%258e%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e6%258f%259233%25e5%2588%2580%25e8%25ac%2580%25e6%25ae%25ba%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%258f%258b-%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%2596%25b9-%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2588%25b6%25e7%258b%2582%25e3%2580%258d%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2591%258a%25e5%2588%2586%25e6%2589%258b%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%2580%25a7%25e6%2584%259b%25e7%2589%2587%25e6%25ae%25b5%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2584%2585%25e4%25ba%258b%25e4%25b8%25bb&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=d4b27bc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00001%2F1603191596513%2F%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%25a8%258b%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e5%2590%25a6%25e8%25aa%258d%25e5%259f%258e%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e6%258f%259233%25e5%2588%2580%25e8%25ac%2580%25e6%25ae%25ba%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%258f%258b-%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%2596%25b9-%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2588%25b6%25e7%258b%2582%25e3%2580%258d%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2591%258a%25e5%2588%2586%25e6%2589%258b%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%2580%25a7%25e6%2584%259b%25e7%2589%2587%25e6%25ae%25b5%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2584%2585%25e4%25ba%258b%25e4%25b8%25bb&h=cde37e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201020/s00001/1603191596513/%e5%b7%a5%e7%a8%8b%e5%b8%ab%e5%90%a6%e8%aa%8d%e5%9f%8e%e5%b7%b4%e6%8f%9233%e5%88%80%e8%ac%80%e6%ae%ba%e5%a5%b3%e5%8f%8b-%e6%8e%a7%e6%96%b9-%e3%80%8c%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6%e7%8b%82%e3%80%8d%e8%a2%ab%e5%91%8a%e5%88%86%e6%89%8b%e5%be%8c%e6%80%a7%e6%84%9b%e7%89%87%e6%ae%b5%e5%a8%81%e8%84%85%e4%ba%8b%e4%b8%bb</a><br />\n城巴車廂2017年發生命案，年輕工程師涉在巴士上持刀狂插女友，女友身中33刀，刀傷遍佈胸腔及肋骨等，送院後不治。男子否認謀殺罪，今（20日）於高等法院受審。控方開案陳辭指出，被告不讓事主參加大學迎新營，又以公開兩人的性愛片段作威脅，事主案發前已提分手。被告後來聲稱，已完全忘記事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的被告吳欣鍵報稱土木工程師，被控於2017年9月16日在香港謀殺李倩姮（20歲，洋名Annie）。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳辭表示，被告與事主同就讀理工大學，於2016年透過手機交友程式相識，後來成為情侶。翌年，事主成功由副學士課程升讀護理系，被告不滿她參加大學迎新營。對事主而言，被告是「控制狂」男友，不但妒忌心重，他亦試圖掌控事主行蹤，事主遂於2017年9月初提分手。被告一度萌生自殺念頭，後來以兩人性愛的片段作威脅，導致事主對被告失去信任。<br />\n<br />\n事發當日，被告乘的士到小西灣，即事主居住的地區。閉路電視拍到被告下午3時在藍灣廣場日本城買入廚刀，然後到巴士站與事主會合，一同乘坐118號城巴。片段顯示，兩人在車上傾談，沒有明顯爭執或打鬥，突然被告取出利刀插向事主身上，及後擊碎車窗跳車，墮地送院。聆訊明（21日）續。"},{"pid":"dc82ea96aeecb808c52807f5e6f1cec598db9500","tid":2250951,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"如果綠帽佳又話焗死條女既時候自己失憶&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f637b4bc58ffc6f50a2bc8120720fa9aa32487","tid":2250951,"uid":289946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"工程毒能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228f8fdc4a48385bfe88d52b2b2ad48af3db0074","tid":2250951,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:44:29.000Z","msg":"ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal